title: reincarnation like plants
pid: 3b1ec9ea-e3b7-4721-b91d-8cf2c96e26eb
body: |2-
  Even without a continuous conscious thread from one life to the next,
  and yet one might recognize oneself the reincarnation of a family member.

  (That might have to only be a statistically especially coincident anomaly --
  we ought to resemble the reincarnation of all family in some proportion.)
